## Workflows

This section defines abstract workflows.

### Weekly Summary Workflow

#### When to call
At the end of the work week.

#### Input
- The previous weekly summary document.
- All documents created between the last summary and today.
- A project background document.

#### Process
1.  Read all input documents.
2.  Synthesize the progress on ongoing projects from the last summary.
3.  Identify newly completed tasks, new ongoing tasks, and new ideas from the new documents.
4.  Structure the new summary following the standard template.
5.  Pay special attention to items marked with `ğŸŸ¥` (TODOs).

